no separate builds per account.<\u002Fp>\n            <div style=\"background:rgba(125,147,140,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(125,147,140,0.15);border-radius:4px;padding:20px 24px;\">\n              <div style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.20em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(125,147,140,0.60);margin-bottom:10px;\">How it works<\u002Fdiv>\n              <p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:400;color:rgba(247,245,241,0.52);line-height:1.80;margin:0;\">Every agent receives a <span style=\"font-family:'Space Grotesk',monospace;color:#7DC1AA;\">clientId<\u002Fspan> on each call. It loads that client's context, runs its skills, and saves outputs to that client's <span style=\"font-family:'Space Grotesk',monospace;color:#7DC1AA;\">/working<\u002Fspan> folder. Same agent. Different context. Every time.<\u002Fp>\n            <\u002Fdiv>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n      <\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n\n  <\u002Fsection>\n\n\n  <!-- ══ SECTION 03 — Capabilities ══ -->\n  <section id=\"capabilities\" style=\"margin-bottom:120px;\">\n\n    <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;margin-bottom:14px;\">\n      <span style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.28em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#7D938C;\">03<\u002Fspan>\n      <div style=\"height:1px;flex:1;background:rgba(4,43,36,0.10);\"><\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n    <div style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.28em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#8B005E;margin-bottom:10px;\">Capabilities → Agent Coverage<\u002Fdiv>\n    <h2 style=\"font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-size:48px;font-weight:400;color:#042B24;letter-spacing:-0.015em;margin:0 0 20px;line-height:1.05;\">Every discipline.<br><span style=\"font-style:italic;\">Every agent.<\u002Fspan><\u002Fh2>\n    <div style=\"width:40px;height:2px;background:#8B005E;border-radius:1px;margin-bottom:28px;\"><\u002Fdiv>\n    <p style=\"font-size:17px;font-weight:400;color:#3A5A52;line-height:1.80;max-width:680px;margin:0 0 56px;\">The OS is built around Poppins' four practice areas. Each discipline maps directly to one or more agents. Adding a new capability means adding one new agent — no structural changes required.<\u002Fp>\n\n    <!-- ── Discipline blocks ── -->\n    <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:32px;\">\n\n      <!-- ═ MARKETING ═ -->\n      <div style=\"border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid rgba(4,43,36,0.08);\">\n        <div style=\"background:#46002F;padding:28px 40px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\">\n          <div style=\"position:absolute;right:0;top:0;bottom:0;width:300px;background:radial-gradient(ellipse at 100% 50%, rgba(139,0,94,0.40) 0%, transparent 70%);pointer-events:none;\"><\u002Fdiv>\n          <div style=\"position:relative;z-index:1;display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:20px;\">\n            <div style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.28em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(227,183,215,0.55);\">Marketing<\u002Fdiv>\n            <div style=\"font-family:'Instrument Serif',serif;font-size:24px;font-style:italic;color:rgba(227,183,215,0.75);\">Community-first marketing<\u002Fdiv>\n          <\u002Fdiv>\n          <p style=\"position:relative;z-index:1;font-size:14px;font-weight:400;color:rgba(247,245,241,0.45);margin:10px 0 0;max-width:700px;line-height:1.70;\">Discovery &amp; strategy, omni-channel campaigns, content production, comms planning. Social insight, influencer engagement, cultural trend analysis.<\u002Fp>\n        <\u002Fdiv>\n        <div style=\"background:#fff;\">\n          <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:196px 1fr 248px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(4,43,36,0.07);padding:12px 40px;background:rgba(4,43,36,0.02);\">\n            <div style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.20em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#7D938C;\">Capability<\u002Fdiv>\n            <div style=\"font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.20em;text-trans